                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360509-1208-offence-1 t18360509-cd-69"></join>6th of April</rs>, 4 watch covers, value 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360509-name-500" type="victimName">
